oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Oak Grove AME Zion Church: cornerstone
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: West, Carroll Van
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Oak Grove African Methodist Episcopal Zion Church and Cemetery
5667 Washington Pike, Knoxville, Knox Co., TN
Black and white photograph of a stone cornerstone in a brick wall reading "A.M.E. Zion Church Oakgrove erec. by J.S. Matthews, Aug 3 1915, Trustees F. Fullwood, J. Graves, W. Johnson."
Oak Grove AME Zion Church was established in 1915.
